author: coffeebank
install_msg:
Thanks for installing, I hope you enjoy :) To stay up to date with breaking changes, you might want to join my Support Discord. To find documentation, Discord, and more, drop by the GitHub repo at <https://github.com/coffeebank/coffee-cogs>

**Setup for bot owners: `[p]setemotes`**
name: emotes
short: Custom emote solution for non-nitro users
description: Custom emote solution for non-nitro users. Use animated emotes in your server, even without Nitro. Make your own emote storage spreadsheet and generate emote-like image links for use in DMs and elsewhere.
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not store any End User Data.
